  <summary>1/8/2003--Introduced.
Amends the Employee Retirement Income Security Act of 1974 (ERISA) to require joint trusteeship of single-employer pension plans, with equal representation of the interests of: (1) the employer or employers maintaining the plan; and (2) the participants and their beneficiaries.</summary>
